{"iti76:0.1":"Itivuttaka 76 ","iti76:0.2":"Tikanipata ","iti76:0.3":"Tatiyavagga ","iti76:0.4":"Sukhapatthanasutta ","iti76:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti76:2.1":"“Tinimani, bhikkhave, sukhani patthayamano silam rakkheyya pandito. ","iti76:2.2":"Katamani tini? ","iti76:2.3":"Pasamsa me agacchatuti silam rakkheyya pandito, bhoga me uppajjantuti silam rakkheyya pandito, kayassa bheda param marana sugatim saggam lokam upapajjissamiti silam rakkheyya pandito. ","iti76:2.4":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, tini sukhani patthayamano silam rakkheyya pandito”ti. ","iti76:2.5":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti76:2.6":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti76:3.1":"“Silam rakkheyya medhavi, ","iti76:3.2":"patthayano tayo sukhe; ","iti76:3.3":"Pasamsam vittalabhanca, ","iti76:3.4":"pecca sagge pamodanam. ","iti76:4.1":"Akarontopi ce papam, ","iti76:4.2":"karontamupasevati; ","iti76:4.3":"Sankiyo hoti papasmim, ","iti76:4.4":"avanno cassa ruhati. ","iti76:5.1":"Yadisam kurute mittam, ","iti76:5.2":"yadisam cupasevati; ","iti76:5.3":"Sa ve tadisako hoti, ","iti76:5.4":"sahavaso hi tadiso. ","iti76:6.1":"Sevamano sevamanam, ","iti76:6.2":"samphuttho samphusam param; ","iti76:6.3":"Saro diddho kalapamva, ","iti76:6.4":"alittamupalimpati; ","iti76:6.5":"Upalepabhaya dhiro, ","iti76:6.6":"neva papasakha siya. ","iti76:7.1":"Putimaccham kusaggena, ","iti76:7.2":"yo naro upanayhati; ","iti76:7.3":"Kusapi puti vayanti, ","iti76:7.4":"evam balupasevana. ","iti76:8.1":"Tagaranca palasena, ","iti76:8.2":"yo naro upanayhati; ","iti76:8.3":"Pattapi surabhi vayanti, ","iti76:8.4":"evam dhirupasevana. ","iti76:9.1":"Tasma pattaputasseva, ","iti76:9.2":"natva sampakamattano; ","iti76:9.3":"Asante nupaseveyya, ","iti76:9.4":"sante seveyya pandito; ","iti76:9.5":"Asanto nirayam nenti, ","iti76:9.6":"santo papenti suggatin”ti. ","iti76:10.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti76:10.2":"Sattamam. "}